msgid "设置浏览器强制使用HTTPS访问"
msgstr "Configures the browser to enforce access over HTTPS"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:201
msgid "max-age: x秒的时间内 访问对应域名都使用HTTPS请求"
msgstr "max-age: for x seconds, use HTTPS requests when accessing the corresponding domain"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:202
msgid "includeSubDomains: 网站的子域名也启用规则"
msgstr "includeSubDomains: also applies the rule to the site's subdomains"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:203
msgid "Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=1000; includeSubDomains"
msgstr "Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=1000; includeSubDomains"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:204
msgid "Trailer"
msgstr "Trailer"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:205
msgid "指出头域在分块传输编码的尾部存在 Trailer: Max-Forwards"
msgstr "Indicates that the header field appears in the trailer of chunked transfer encoding. Trailer: Max-Forwards"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:206
msgid "Transfer-Encoding"
msgstr "Transfer-Encoding"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:207
msgid "文件传输编码"
msgstr "File transfer encoding"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:208
msgid "Transfer-Encoding:chunked"
msgstr "Transfer-Encoding:chunked"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:209
msgid "Vary"
msgstr "Vary"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:210
msgid "告诉下游代理是使用缓存响应还是从原始服务器请求"
msgstr "Tells downstream proxies whether to use a cached response or request from the origin server"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:211
msgid "Vary: *"
msgstr "Vary: *"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:213
msgid "告知代理客户端响应是通过哪里发送的"
msgstr "Tells proxies where the client response was sent through"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:216
msgid "警告实体可能存在的问题"
msgstr "Warns about possible problems with the entity"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:217
msgid "Warning: 199 Miscellaneous warning"
msgstr "Warning: 199 Miscellaneous warning"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:218
msgid "WWW-Authenticate"
msgstr "WWW-Authenticate"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:219
msgid "表明客户端请求实体应该使用的授权方案"
msgstr "Indicates the authorization scheme the client should use for the requested entity"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:220
msgid "WWW-Authenticate: Basic"
msgstr "WWW-Authenticate: Basic"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:221
msgid "X-Content-Type-Options"
msgstr "X-Content-Type-Options"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:222
msgid "配置禁止MIME类型嗅探"
msgstr "Configures MIME type sniffing prevention"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:223
msgid "X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff"
msgstr "X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:224
msgid "X-Frame-Options"
msgstr "X-Frame-Options"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:225
msgid "配置页面是否能出现在 <frame>, <iframe>, <embed>, <object> 等标签中，防止点击劫持"
msgstr "Configures whether the page can appear in tags such as <frame>, <iframe>, <embed>, and <object> to prevent clickjacking"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:226
msgid "X-Frame-Options: deny"
msgstr "X-Frame-Options: deny"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:227
msgid "X-XSS-Protection"
msgstr "X-XSS-Protection"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:228
msgid "配置XSS防护机制"
msgstr "Configures the XSS protection mechanism"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:229
msgid "X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block"
msgstr "X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:232
msgid "HTTP状态返回代码 1xx（临时响应）"
msgstr "HTTP Status Codes 1xx (Informational Responses)"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:233
msgid "表示临时响应并需要请求者继续执行操作的状态代码。"
msgstr "Status codes that indicate a temporary response and require the requester to continue the operation."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:236
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:247
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:263
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:279
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:305
msgid "Code"
msgstr "Code"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:236
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:247
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:263
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:279
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:305
msgid "代码"
msgstr "Status"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:236
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:247
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:263
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:279
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:305
msgid "说明"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:238
msgid "100"
msgstr "100"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:238
msgid "继续"
msgstr "Continue"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:238
msgid "服务器返回此代码表示已收到请求的第一部分，正在等待其余部分"
msgstr "The server returns this code to indicate that it has received the first part of the request and is waiting for the rest"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:239
msgid "101"
msgstr "101"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:239
msgid "切换协议"
msgstr "Switching Protocols"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:239
msgid "请求者已要求服务器切换协议，服务器已确认并准备切换"
msgstr "The requester asked the server to switch protocols, and the server has confirmed and is ready to switch"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:243
msgid "HTTP状态返回代码 2xx （成功）"
msgstr "HTTP Status Codes 2xx (Success)"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:244
msgid "表示成功处理了请求的状态代码。"
msgstr "Status codes indicating that the request was processed successfully."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:249
msgid "200"
msgstr "200"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:249
msgid "成功"
msgstr "OK"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:249
msgid "服务器已成功处理了请求。 通常，这表示服务器提供了请求的网页"
msgstr "The server successfully processed the request. Usually, this means the server provided the requested web page"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:250
msgid "201"
msgstr "201"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:250
msgid "已创建"
msgstr "Created"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:250
msgid "请求成功并且服务器创建了新的资源"
msgstr "The request succeeded and the server created a new resource"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:251
msgid "202"
msgstr "202"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:251
msgid "已接受"
msgstr "Accepted"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:251
msgid "服务器已接受请求，但尚未处理"
msgstr "The server accepted the request but has not processed it yet"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:252
msgid "203"
msgstr "203"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:252
msgid "非授权信息"
msgstr "Non-Authoritative Information"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:252
msgid "服务器已成功处理了请求，但返回的信息可能来自另一来源"
msgstr "The server successfully processed the request, but the returned information may come from another source"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:253
msgid "204"
msgstr "204"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:253
msgid "无内容"
msgstr "No Content"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:253
msgid "服务器成功处理了请求，但没有返回任何内容"
msgstr "The server successfully processed the request but returned no content"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:254
msgid "205"
msgstr "205"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:254
msgid "重置内容"
msgstr "Reset Content"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:254
msgid "m服务器成功处理了请求，但没有返回任何内容"
msgstr "The server successfully processed the request but returned no content"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:255
msgid "206"
msgstr "206"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:255
msgid "部分内容"
msgstr "Partial Content"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:255
msgid "服务器成功处理了部分GET请求"
msgstr "The server successfully processed a partial GET request"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:259
msgid "HTTP状态返回代码 3xx （重定向）"
msgstr "HTTP Status Codes 3xx (Redirection)"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:260
msgid "表示要完成请求，需要进一步操作。 通常，这些状态代码用来重定向。"
msgstr "Status codes indicating that further action is required to complete the request. These status codes are usually used for redirection."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:265
msgid "300"
msgstr "300"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:265
msgid "多种选择"
msgstr "Multiple Choices"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:265
msgid "针对请求，服务器可执行多种操作。 服务器可根据请求者 (user agent) 选择一项操作，或提供操作列表供请求者选择。"
msgstr "For the request, the server can perform multiple actions. The server may choose an action based on the requester (user agent), or provide a list of actions for the requester to choose from."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:266
msgid "301"
msgstr "301"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:266
msgid "永久移动"
msgstr "Moved Permanently"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:266
msgid "请求的网页已永久移动到新位置。 服务器返回此响应（对 GET 或 HEAD 请求的响应）时，会自动将请求者转到新位置。"
msgstr "The requested web page has moved permanently to a new location. When the server returns this response to a GET or HEAD request, it automatically redirects the requester to the new location."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:267
msgid "302"
msgstr "302"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:267
msgid "临时移动"
msgstr "Found"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:267
#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:271
msgid "服务器目前从不同位置的网页响应请求，但请求者应继续使用原有位置来进行以后的请求。"
msgstr "The server is currently responding to the request with a web page from a different location, but the requester should continue using the original location for future requests."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:268
msgid "303"
msgstr "303"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:268
msgid "查看其他位置"
msgstr "See Other"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:268
msgid "请求者应当对不同的位置使用单独的 GET 请求来检索响应时，服务器返回此代码。"
msgstr "The server returns this code when the requester should use a separate GET request to retrieve the response from a different location."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:269
msgid "304"
msgstr "304"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:269
msgid "未修改"
msgstr "Not Modified"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:269
msgid "自从上次请求后，请求的网页未修改过。 服务器返回此响应时，不会返回网页内容。"
msgstr "The requested web page has not been modified since the last request. When the server returns this response, it does not return the page content."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:270
msgid "305"
msgstr "305"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:270
msgid "使用代理"
msgstr "Use Proxy"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:270
msgid "请求者只能使用代理访问请求的网页。如果服务器返回此响应，还表示请求者应使用代理。"
msgstr "The requester can access the requested web page only through a proxy. If the server returns this response, it also indicates that the requester should use a proxy."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:271
msgid "307"
msgstr "307"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:271
msgid "临时重定向"
msgstr "Temporary Redirect"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:275
msgid "HTTP状态返回代码 4xx（请求错误）"
msgstr "HTTP Status Codes 4xx (Request Errors)"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:276
msgid "这些状态代码表示请求可能出错，妨碍了服务器的处理。"
msgstr "These status codes indicate that the request may contain an error that prevents the server from processing it."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:281
msgid "400"
msgstr "400"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:281
msgid "错误请求"
msgstr "Bad Request"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:281
msgid "服务器不理解请求的语法。"
msgstr "The server does not understand the request syntax."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:282
msgid "401"
msgstr "401"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:282
msgid "未授权"
msgstr "Unauthorized"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:282
msgid "请求要求身份验证。对于需要登录的网页，服务器可能返回此响应。"
msgstr "The request requires authentication. For pages that require login, the server may return this response."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:283
msgid "403"
msgstr "403"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:283
msgid "禁止"
msgstr "Forbidden"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:283
msgid "服务器拒绝请求。"
msgstr "The server refused the request."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:284
msgid "404"
msgstr "404"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:284
msgid "未找到"
msgstr "Not Found"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:284
msgid "服务器找不到请求的网页。"
msgstr "The server cannot find the requested web page."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:285
msgid "405"
msgstr "405"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:285
msgid "方法禁用"
msgstr "Method Not Allowed"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:285
msgid "禁用请求中指定的方法。"
msgstr "The method specified in the request is disabled."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:286
msgid "406"
msgstr "406"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:286
msgid "不接受"
msgstr "Not Acceptable"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:286
msgid "无法使用请求的内容特性响应请求的网页。"
msgstr "The requested web page cannot be returned using the content characteristics requested."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:287
msgid "407"
msgstr "407"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:287
msgid "需要代理授权"
msgstr "Proxy Authentication Required"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:287
msgid "此状态代码与 401（未授权）类似，但指定请求者应当授权使用代理。"
msgstr "This status code is similar to 401 (Unauthorized), but specifies that the requester must authenticate with a proxy."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:288
msgid "408"
msgstr "408"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:288
msgid "请求超时"
msgstr "Request Timeout"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:288
msgid "服务器等候请求时发生超时。"
msgstr "The server timed out while waiting for the request."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:289
msgid "409"
msgstr "409"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:289
msgid "冲突"
msgstr "Conflict"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:289
msgid "服务器在完成请求时发生冲突。 服务器必须在响应中包含有关冲突的信息。"
msgstr "The server encountered a conflict while completing the request. The server must include information about the conflict in the response."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:290
msgid "410"
msgstr "410"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:290
msgid "已删除"
msgstr "Gone"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:290
msgid "如果请求的资源已永久删除，服务器就会返回此响应。"
msgstr "The server returns this response if the requested resource has been permanently deleted."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:291
msgid "411"
msgstr "411"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:291
msgid "需要有效长度"
msgstr "Length Required"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:291
msgid "服务器不接受不含有效内容长度标头字段的请求。"
msgstr "The server does not accept requests without a valid Content-Length header field."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:292
msgid "412"
msgstr "412"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:292
msgid "未满足前提条件"
msgstr "Precondition Failed"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:292
msgid "服务器未满足请求者在请求中设置的其中一个前提条件。"
msgstr "The server did not meet one of the preconditions set by the requester in the request."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:293
msgid "413"
msgstr "413"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:293
msgid "请求实体过大"
msgstr "Request Entity Too Large"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:293
msgid "服务器无法处理请求，因为请求实体过大，超出服务器的处理能力。"
msgstr "The server cannot process the request because the request entity is too large and exceeds the server's processing capacity."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:294
msgid "414"
msgstr "414"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:294
msgid "请求的 URI 过长"
msgstr "Request URI Too Long"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:294
msgid "请求的 URI（通常为网址）过长，服务器无法处理。"
msgstr "The requested URI, usually a URL, is too long for the server to process."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:295
msgid "415"
msgstr "415"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:295
msgid "不支持的媒体类型"
msgstr "Unsupported Media Type"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:295
msgid "请求的格式不受请求页面的支持。"
msgstr "The request format is not supported by the requested page."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:296
msgid "416"
msgstr "416"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:296
msgid "请求范围不符合要求"
msgstr "Requested Range Not Satisfiable"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:296
msgid "如果页面无法提供请求的范围，则服务器会返回此状态代码。"
msgstr "The server returns this status code if the page cannot provide the requested range."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:297
msgid "417"
msgstr "417"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:297
msgid "未满足期望值"
msgstr "Expectation Failed"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:297
msgid "服务器未满足\"期望\"请求标头字段的要求。"
msgstr "The server did not meet the requirements of the \"Expect\" request header field."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:301
msgid "HTTP状态返回代码 5xx（服务器错误）"
msgstr "HTTP Status Codes 5xx (Server Errors)"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:302
msgid "这些状态代码表示服务器在尝试处理请求时发生内部错误。 这些错误可能是服务器本身的错误，而不是请求出错。"
msgstr "These status codes indicate that the server encountered an internal error while trying to process the request. These errors may be server-side errors rather than request errors."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:307
msgid "500"
msgstr "500"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:307
msgid "服务器内部错误"
msgstr "Internal Server Error"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:307
msgid "服务器遇到错误，无法完成请求。"
msgstr "The server encountered an error and could not complete the request."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:308
msgid "501"
msgstr "501"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:308
msgid "尚未实施"
msgstr "Not Implemented"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:308
msgid "服务器不具备完成请求的功能。例如，服务器无法识别请求方法时可能会返回此代码。"
msgstr "The server does not have the functionality required to complete the request. For example, it may return this code when it cannot recognize the request method."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:309
msgid "502"
msgstr "502"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:309
msgid "错误网关"
msgstr "Bad Gateway"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:309
msgid "服务器作为网关或代理，从上游服务器收到无效响应。"
msgstr "The server, acting as a gateway or proxy, received an invalid response from an upstream server."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:310
msgid "503"
msgstr "503"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:310
msgid "服务不可用"
msgstr "Service Unavailable"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:310
msgid "服务器目前无法使用（由于超载或停机维护）。 通常，这只是暂时状态。"
msgstr "The server is currently unavailable because it is overloaded or down for maintenance. Usually, this is only temporary."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:311
msgid "504"
msgstr "504"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:311
msgid "网关超时"
msgstr "Gateway Timeout"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:311
msgid "服务器作为网关或代理，但是没有及时从上游服务器收到请求。"
msgstr "The server, acting as a gateway or proxy, did not receive a timely response from the upstream server."

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:312
msgid "505"
msgstr "505"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:312
msgid "HTTP 版本不受支持"
msgstr "HTTP Version Not Supported"

#: ../../source/network/http/http.rst:312
msgid "服务器不支持请求中所用的 HTTP 协议版本。"
msgstr "The server does not support the HTTP protocol version used in the request."
